-- Valeo to Invest as Much as $625 Million in China by 2015, Les Echos Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-05T05:05:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/valeo-to-invest-as-much-as-625-million-in-china-by-2015-les-echos-says.html

          
          
             Valeo SA plans to invest between 400
million and 500 million euros in China by 2015, French daily Les
Echos reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Jacques
Aschenbroich.  
 The company aims to double its Chinese sales by 2013 from
460 million euros last year, the newspaper said.  
          
          


  


        